data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is nicely situated on an oversize lot in the desired Palm Harbor Subdivision! Large eat-in kitchen, stainless appliances, subway tile backsplash, granite counters, glass front cabinets. Floor to ceiling bookshelves in the pass-through library. Guest bath mural by a local artist. Master has walk-in shower, walk-in closet, & separate 2nd sink outside the full master bath French doors from the kitchen & master lead to a large air conditioned Florida room with 2 sliders and a side door. Replaced flooring throughout. Fully fenced yard has a firepit for your evening enjoyment! Roof replaced in 2008 Current mortgage is an assumable low-rate VA mortgage - a great opportunity for VA qualified buyers!
